---
title: Beyond Meat® Chili and Baked Potato Bowls with Sour Cream and Peppers
description: Loaded nachos and loaded baked potatoes blend in this bowl! Cubed and roasted yellow potatoes are topped with a savoury Beyond Meat® chili, and we've added the classic nacho fixings – sour cream, cheddar cheese, chopped tomatoes and green onions.

